Design Philosophy

The engine does not replace investigators.

It augments them.

Its purpose is not certainty.

Its purpose is disciplined convergence toward reality.

Every reconstruction remains traceable.

Every inference remains challengeable.

Every unknown remains visible.

Reality is treated as an evolving model constrained by evidence, never as an unquestionable generated narrative.

‚∏ª

Canonical Closing

Reality leaves fingerprints everywhere.

No observer sees the whole.

But every observer leaves a stroke on the canvas.

The Reality Reconstruction Engine exists to gather those strokes, preserve their provenance, acknowledge their uncertainty, and reconstruct the most faithful world the evidence can support‚Äîone brushstroke at a time.